product_name: Anastasia Beverly HillsFull-Pigment Matte & Satin Velvet Lipstick
summary: SummaryHighlightsCruelty FreeThe ABH Matte & Satin Lipstick is perfection in a single swipe: brilliantly pigmented and incredibly smooth glide-on, stunning shades in two featherlight finishes, and effortless control with ease. It’s made for all your looks day to night, natural to glam.
details: DetailsBenefitsFull-pigment, weightless color that lastsUltra-smooth formulas with comfortable wearability (no feathering)Satin finish delivers luminous color and cushion-like texture (not slippery or sticky)Matte finish delivers creamy, true-matte color and velvety-soft texture (not dry or waxy)Precise bullet shape effortlessly glides and defines lipsDelivers full pigment in one swipe that applies evenly and seamlesslyVersatile shade range with cool, warm, and neutral undertonesLuxe, rose-gold packagingDermatologist testedFree of: parabens, phthalates, sulfate, oil, mineral oil, alcohol, talcItem 2604144How To UseBegin by outlining the cupid's bow. Fill in the remainder of the top lip. Outline the bottom lip and fill.PRO TIPS:Pair with Lip Liner for a sculpted and defined look.For further definition, apply Pro Pencil around the perimeter of the lips and blend with Brush 20.Pair with Brush 3 to further define the lip shape or detail the lips with precision.Diffuse the lip line with a small amount of Pro Pencil on Brush 18 for a soft, diffused look.For dry lips, prep using Lip Primer before application.IngredientsDimethicone, Octyldodecanol, Polyethylene, Polysilicone-11, Nylon-12, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Bis-Peg-12 Dimethicone Beeswax, Methyl Methacrylate Crosspolymer, Dicalcium Phosphate, Stearalkonium Bentonite, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Propylene Carbonate, Ethyl Vanillin, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-Di-T-Butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Laureth-12, Mica, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492), Blue 1 Lake (CI 42090), Red 7 Lake (CI 15850)Shipping & Coupon RestrictionsThis brand is excluded from most Ulta Beauty coupons.See brand eligibility details
how_to_use: Begin by outlining the cupid's bow. Fill in the remainder of the top lip. Outline the bottom lip and fill.PRO TIPS:Pair with Lip Liner for a sculpted and defined look.For further definition, apply Pro Pencil around the perimeter of the lips and blend with Brush 20.Pair with Brush 3 to further define the lip shape or detail the lips with precision.Diffuse the lip line with a small amount of Pro Pencil on Brush 18 for a soft, diffused look.For dry lips, prep using Lip Primer before application.

reviews.headline: Love this long lasting beautiful color
reviews.comments: This is the perfect shade of pink. The lipstick goes on smooth and makes my lips feel great. I would definitely buy it again and recommend it to others.

reviews.headline: CAME MELTED!!!
reviews.comments: Ordered two...one cam melted. Went to the Orange CT store to exchange but they didn't have it. Sales Associate explained they would refund me the sale price & then charge full price to reorder!!! DO BETTER FOR YOUR CUSTOMERS ULTA!!!!

reviews.headline: I will buy this product again also in other shades
reviews.comments: It is such a good lipstick. The color I love, the texture is nice. It is light.

reviews.headline: I love it
reviews.comments: It stays on longer than  new mac 24 lipstick… it feels amazing.  It's moisturizing!!  Make darker colors please

reviews.headline: Love the color, keeps breaking.
reviews.comments: I gave this 3 stars because I LOVE the blush brown color, however the last two lipsticks I have bought have broke at the base and is hard to use. They never used to do this.

reviews.headline: I would buy this product again.
reviews.comments: This is my second Anastasia BH lip color. This time in Sun Baked. Just ordered the lip liner too. This is a non-drying matte which I love and it lasts a long time. I have had several compliments on the color and people asking what brand lipstick it is.

reviews.headline: Love it!
reviews.comments: I love the richness of the formula, the color was exactly what i wanted for that warm nude filler. Perfect matte and not drying at all. I ended up buying two one for my purse and one to keep in my makeup vanity.

reviews.headline: Silky smooth
reviews.comments: Silky and smooth on my lips. Great color. Wish it lasted longer as an avid water drinker.

reviews.headline: Royal red
reviews.comments: Royal red is a great red blue. It's soft, not drying, and the perfect color. American doll is an orange red fyi. I'm a true winter, lighter skin and so the red blue is more complimentary.

reviews.headline: Misleading
reviews.comments: I bought Sun Baked because it looks like a pretty shade of pink.  This color looks absolutely nothing like the photos.  It's this terrible shade of dark brown. I hate it so much.

reviews.headline: Sparkle
reviews.comments: I love the color and sparkle

reviews.headline: American Doll is orange red
reviews.comments: This appeared blue red and reviews suggested such. It definitely is not, will be returning.

reviews.headline: Awesome lips
reviews.comments: Fabulous color

reviews.headline: Perfect subtle color.
reviews.comments: This is my go to daytime lipstick I use a bit darker liner for a fresh natural look. My only comment is this is not the cleanest product. I wish they would use more natural products but I think that is somewhat hard to do to make a lipstick stable. I do recommend it. It's pretty and it stays on well.

reviews.headline: Is not long wearing
reviews.comments: The worst "long lasting" lipstick ever.

reviews.headline: Love it
reviews.comments: Loved color and application

reviews.headline: Why is no one online talking about this?!
reviews.comments:
This lipstick is absolutely gorgeous! I can only attest to the matte formula, as I only have the shade "Sugar Plum." Granted, the name is deceiving, as this is more like a reddish brown, but that's exactly what I was looking for anyway. 
This is smooth, pigmented, non-drying, and when blotted, quite long-lasting. It doesn't emphasize my deeper lip lines and doesn't feather or bleed. No scent, which is great because even a sweet smell can be cloying. 
I'll be picking up "Rum Punch" next because if it performs as well as "Sugar Plum," I know I'll be happy.

reviews.headline: I wanted to buy it again
reviews.comments: It looks so pretty! I love it

reviews.headline: sticky consistency.
reviews.comments: will not be using this. the consistency is terrible, feels tacky on the lips.

faceoff_positive.comments: Wow, this lipstick is so creamy and hydrating and at 41 it actually surprised me. With one swipe It literally just melted into my lips and left them feeling amazingly soft. The lipstick case Itself is so beautiful and sleek that it's almost to pretty to use. I was able to get a precise line when applying this to my lips and the color payoff is insane. First swipe and my lips looked beautiful and plump. I do overdraw my lips but everything looked even and with no smearing. I'm truely amazed by this lipstick and I suggest pairing it with the matching lip liner for that all nighter intense look. I definitely found a new favorite and to think I almost decided to give up on lipstick!
faceoff_positive.headline: So hydrating and creamy!

faceoff_negative.comments:
ABH auburn lipstick is a beautiful color. It pulls quite red on me. I am sad to say I do not care for this lipstick. It is very hard to get right the first time. I feel like it deposits everywhere even with being careful. It is hard to get a precise application. Reapplying is necessary because after applying the fade off is not equal and looks bizarre. 

Even with proper moisturizing and exfoliating of the lips. I do feel my lips look dry and it is does stain the lips or skin so please beware.
faceoff_negative.headline: Extremely hard to get right
